diaspora-voting/          ← your project folder name
│
├── app/
│   ├── page.tsx          ← your landing page (the JSX I built)
│   ├── layout.tsx        ← root layout (boilerplate)
│   └── api/
│       ├── sign/
│       │   └── route.ts  ← API: receives form → saves to Airtable
│       └── stats/
│           └── route.ts  ← API: returns live sig + download counts
│
├── .env.local            ← your secret keys (never commit this)
├── package.json
└── next.config.js